 Non-invasive Neurostimulation of the Vagus Nerve for the Treatment of Cluster Headache@highlight

Multi-center, prospective, double-blind, randomized, sham-controlled pivotal study of non-invasive vagus nerve stimulation with the GammaCore(R) device for the acute treatment of cluster headache.

 The study compares the safety and effectiveness of an active treatment (GammaCore) against a sham treatment.

